title: VIP Club party room, Walk-in Closets
posting_body: ["Sky's The Limit", 'The Vermont fashions a new paradigm of style, serenity and service.', 'Defined by its beautiful views, extensive amenities and an attention to detail that solidifies its status as a unique, high-end living experience on the Wilshire Corridor.', 'Located seven stories above the city, a creatively imagined, expansive garden, heated swimming pool, deck, spa and dog park are all available year round to enjoy the 24/7/365 Southern California climate.', "With high-end design and services unmatched among apartment rentals, The Vermont sets itself apart as a signature property in LA's Koreatown community.", 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'Follow This Link for More Information:', '<URL>', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 1007 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Floor to Ceiling Glass Windows', '- The luxury of more space', '- Euro Style Cabinetry', '- Toto Fixtures', '- Granite Countertops', '- Walk-in Closets', '- Stainless-Steel Appliances', '- Breathtaking 180° views', '- Bosch Washer/Dryer', 'Community Amenities', '- Expansive seventh story garden', '- Spectacular heated Pool and Spa', '- The Drop Lounge', '- VIP Club party room', '- On-site casual and gourmet restaurants', '- Across from the Metro Purple/Red Line station.', '- Five Star service all around', '- Fit 360 Private full gym access', '- Dramatic SkyBridge lobby', '- Banking, Barista / Coffee service on-site', '- Dog Park', 'Pet Policy', 'Pet Friendly!*', 'The Vermont', '3150 Wilsire Blvd., Los Angeles, CA, 90010', 'Greystar California, Inc., Broker License #01525765', 'DMCA Agent: <URL>', 'MMaQ21rToCd8']
